      "bookmarkId": "812680_6_513-561",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "513-561",
      "markText": "张居正总结说：人们怕那些吏，一定要贿赂那些吏，并不是指望从他们手里捞点好处，而是怕他们祸害自己。",
      "totalCount": 6896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=812680&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=513&rangeEnd=561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03b32a705c668803be75fde?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=513&rangeEnd=561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "812680_5_1125-1221",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1125-1221",
      "markText": "中国社会在正式规定的各种制度之外，在种种明文规定的背后，实际存在着一个不成文的又获得广泛认可的规矩，一种可以称为内部章程的东西。恰恰是这种东西，而不是冠冕堂皇的正式规定，支配着现实生活的运行。",
      "totalCount": 6495,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=812680&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1125&rangeEnd=1221",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03b32a705c668803be75fde?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1125&rangeEnd=1221"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "812680_10_8530-8558",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "8530-8558",
      "markText": "帝国制度很善于把常人难免的弱点和毛病培育为全国性的灾难。",
      "totalCount": 5831,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=812680&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8530&rangeEnd=8558",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03b32a705c668803be75fde?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8530&rangeEnd=8558"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "812680_6_586-637",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "586-637",
      "markText": "合法地祸害别人的能力，乃是官吏们的看家本领。这是一门真正的艺术，种种资源和财富正要据此分肥并重新调整。",
      "totalCount": 5538,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=812680&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=586&rangeEnd=637",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03b32a705c668803be75fde?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=586&rangeEnd=637"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "812680_10_5797-5861",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5797-5861",
      "markText": "一个变质的政府，一个剥削性的越来越强，服务性越来越弱的政府，自然也需要变质的官员，需要他们泯灭良心，心狠手辣，否则就要请你走人。",
      "totalCount": 5490,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=812680&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5797&rangeEnd=5861",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03b32a705c668803be75fde?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5797&rangeEnd=5861"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "812680_7_7584-7650",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7584-7650",
      "markText": "个体狼的利益与狼群的集体利益未必一致。如果我的节制不能导致别人的节制，我的自我约束对羊群来说就没有任何意义，徒然减少自己的份额而已。",
      "totalCount": 4420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=812680&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7584&rangeEnd=7650",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03b32a705c668803be75fde?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7584&rangeEnd=7650"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "812680_8_6169-6202",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6169-6202",
      "markText": "可见没有垄断地位的洋人拿了钱是真干活的，并不像清朝水师那样卖假货。",
      "totalCount": 3776,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=812680&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6169&rangeEnd=6202",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/03b32a705c668803be75fde?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6169&rangeEnd=6202"
    },
    {
